<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>MizuiChanBot PRE-ALPHA</title>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1a1a2e, #0f0f0f 60%, #000);
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .glow {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: url("https://img.magnific.com/free-photo/illustration-cosmic-background-with-orange-neon-laser-lights_181624-19567.jpg?semt=ais_hybrid&w=740&q=80");
      opacity: 0.05;
      animation: move 20s linear infinite;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    @keyframes move {
      from { transform: translateY(0); }
      to { transform: translateY(-200px); }
    }

    /* 🦖 GODZILLA */
    .godzilla {
      width: 380px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(0,255,255,0.4));
    }

    /* TITULO GRANDE */
    h1 {
      font-size: 70px; /* 🔥 maior */
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-top: 10px;
      text-shadow:
        0 0 20px #00fff0,
        0 0 40px #ff00ff,
        0 0 60px #0066ff;
    }

    /* DESCRIÇÃO CENTRAL */
    p {
      max-width: 750px;
      font-size: 36px; /* 🔥 maior */
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .monarch {
      font-size: 100px;
      letter-spacing: 0px;
      color: #00fff0;
      opacity: 0.8;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    /* BOTÕES ABAIXO DA DESCRIÇÃO */
    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 60px 90px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff7a00, #7a00ff, #00c3ff);
      color: black;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 28px;
      text-decoration: none;
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,255,240,0.6);
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: scale(1.1);
      box-shadow: 0 0 70px rgba(255,0,255,0.8);
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="glow"></div>

  <div class="monarch">21/05/26 Experimental</div>

  <!-- TITULO -->
  <h1>MizuiChann PRE-ALPHA Oficial</h1>

  <!-- DESCRIÇÃO CENTRAL -->
  <p>
    MizuiChan É um bot criado por um adolescente.
    Bot criado no dia 19/05/26, PRE-ALPHA(bugs,criticas, bot em observação).
  </p>

  <!-- BOTÕES EMBAIXO -->
  <div class="buttons">

    <a class="btn" href="https://discord.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=1506668863734157402&permissions=8&integration_type=0&scope=bot" target="_blank">
      ADD BOT
    </a>

    <a class="btn" href="https://discord.gg/XfMne2nfM" target="_blank">
      INVITE SERVER
    </a>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
